description:
&lt;p&gt;We are developing an exciting career development pathway for experienced MSK APP to help shape the future of the service and develop their clinical skills. The APP role supports the clinical delivery of the North Hampshire MSK service. The MSK service encompasses. Physiotherapy MSK Podiatry Community Triage (APP/GPSI)Orthopaedic Surgery&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The purpose of the APP role is to work as an autonomous APP providing expert musculoskeletal assessments, clinical diagnosis and management in an advanced role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role of the APP Team Lead has additional responsibilities that include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Time to be split 0.7 clinical and 0.3 managerial/admin&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Direct Line management of the APP team cascading line management via senior APP’s for more junior APP’s. Line managing no more than 5 staff members&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dealing with queries and gatekeeping relating to the APP service&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deputising for Clinical Lead or Pathway Lead when appropriate&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Person Specification:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;experience with experience as an APP&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Relevant evidence of CPD&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Member of HCPC and CSP&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Degree in physiotherapy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working in a musculoskeletal setting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Additional benefits of joining Circle Health:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;27 days’ annual leave with additional days for long-term service pro rata&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cycle to work scheme: save money on a new bike and benefit from interest-free instalments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Private pension scheme helping your to live well in retirement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Health and wellbeing programme which includes free fruit, massages and fitness sessions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Employee assistance programme: get confidential support 24/7&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Private medical insurance to help you get any treatment you need quickly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Non-contributory life assurance and income protection insurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perkbox for employee discounts at a range of retailers, restaurants and other services&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free Uniform&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Season ticket loan: get the benefit of an annual ticket and pay the cost over 12 months&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
